{"tid":1357433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"臨時政府係咪香港唯一出路","createTime":"2019-07-23T17:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T00:13:35.000Z","uid":58841,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"188c1cce8b95a2caf816322071a9c878a1188510","tid":1357433,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:13:28.000Z","msg":"臨時政府係新舊政府之間既過渡期<br />\n不過要注意<br />\n並唔係所有野都要reset<br />\n就我黎要reset只有三樣野：<br />\n1 立法會<br />\n重新組織新成員 即係真普選<br />\n2 警隊 <br />\n目前香港有警隊人數過多同招募標準過多問題 要全面改革<br />\n體能標準要同消防 海關體能看齊 唔可以太低<br />\n要加埋筆試 可以參考台灣警專兩年培訓 同埋警大<br />\n3 醫管局"},{"pid":"9d230c72f8761ac3530cdfc169a0649df1301e67","tid":1357433,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:13:49.000Z","msg":"[知己知彼]進入三毛思考領域，請連仔幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224185</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推上熱門"},{"pid":"1dd503927b7e504576b79db3c8c2f50a2ab1f1f5","tid":1357433,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:13:57.000Z","msg":"726 機場 - [突發] 7月26 香港國際機場集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354319</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n727 元朗 （重點）- 元朗遊行已遞交不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355504</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n728 上環 （新增）-【毋忘上環】7.28上環追究開槍大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n84 將軍澳 - 【正式宣布】8月4日 舉行 「將軍澳反送中大遊行」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356143</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5265519c280d6da8caaa7d32f43d07198c3aa793","tid":1357433,"uid":219444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:14:59.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"0e91aa1a5452fdc463a440cc641ae44a82c7abdb","tid":1357433,"ui